Task: 
====
1. Install cronie package
2. Add a cron */5 * * * * echo hello > tmp/cron_text 

" Login to App 01 Server
$ ssh tony@stapp01
$ sudo su

" Install cronie package
# yum install cronie -y

" Start and check cron service
# systemctl start crond.service
# systemctl status crond.service

" Create cron job
# crontab -e
 in the vi editor type 

*/5 * * * * echo hello > tmp/cron_text 

" Check cron job
# cronjob -labels

" Check cron job for root
# crontab -u root -l


Repeat for other App Servers 
